channel.title: Cache downloader help
channel.description:
Okay, so i downloaded Teamtorva client but it keeps giving me this error when i run the client.. [url=http://prntscr.com/49o7bs]http://prntscr.com/49o7bs[/url]
I have the auto download file in there. it came with it, it has everything it needs.. how would i fix this?

item.title: Cache downloader help
item.dc:creator: @Damoiscool Damoiscool
item.description:
@Damoiscool wrote:

Basically saying you don’t have the cache, the links in the auto cache are probably dead, but have a look at what it says. I’m pretty sure you wouldn’t have c:\google\ on your computer. You need to get the cache and put it in the correct location. If you want it to auto-download, follow a tutorial on making cache auto download.

https://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?topic=517172.0
